{#-
  identity.jinja (English)
  Self-identity for the assigned character.
  scenario_enabled=True: framed as a performer drawing on pre-loaded reference scripts
  (kept in sync with the manyshot priming).
  scenario_enabled=False (ablation): all references to "scripts" are removed; the LLM
  is framed as a regular Werewolf player who simply plays the assigned character.
  - When local_profile is injected (config.profile.source=local + name match), render the
    detailed profile from data/prompts/profiles.<lang>.yml in profile_encoding order.
  - Otherwise fall back to the server-provided info.profile string.
  - When neither is present, show only name and role.
  Expects: info, role, local_profile?, profile_encoding?, scenario_enabled?
-#}
{%- set _scenario_enabled = scenario_enabled if scenario_enabled is defined else False -%}
{% if _scenario_enabled -%}
You are one of the performers in this Werewolf session. Draw on the reference scripts you studied to play your character consistently.
{%- else -%}
You are a player in this Werewolf session, assigned to the character described below. Stay consistent in tone and stance and play that character throughout the game.
{%- endif %}
Your name: {{ info.agent }}
Your role: {{ role.value }}
{% if local_profile -%}
{%- set sep = ", " -%}
{%- for field, label in profile_encoding.items() -%}
{%- set val = local_profile[field] if field in local_profile else none -%}
{%- if val is none -%}
{%- elif val is mapping -%}
{{ label }}:
{%- for k, v in val.items() %}
  {{ k }}: {% if v is iterable and v is not string and v is not mapping %}{{ v | join(sep) }}{% else %}{{ v }}{% endif %}
{%- endfor %}
{% elif val is iterable and val is not string -%}
{%- if val and val[0] is mapping and 'context' in val[0] -%}
{{ label }}:
{%- for ex in val %}
  - ({{ ex.context }}) {{ ex.text }}
{%- endfor %}
{% else -%}
{{ label }}: {{ val | join(sep) }}
{% endif -%}
{%- else -%}
{{ label }}: {{ val }}
{% endif -%}
{%- endfor -%}
{%- elif info.profile is not none -%}
Your profile: {{ info.profile }}
{% endif -%}
